      "options": [
        "1.5",
        "2.0",
        "2.5",
        "3.0"
      ],
      "explanation": "Numerator: 3/4 + 2/4 = 5/4. Denominator: 5/6 - 2/6 = 3/6 = 1/2. Result = (5/4) / (1/2) = 5/4 x 2 = 10/4 = 2.5."
    },
    "hi": {
      "question": "सरल करें: (3/4 + 1/2) / (5/6 - 1/3)",
      "options": [
        "1.5",
        "2.0",
        "2.5",
        "3.0"
      ],
      "explanation": "अंश: 3/4 + 2/4 = 5/4। हर: 5/6 - 2/6 = 3/6 = 1/2। परिणाम = (5/4) / (1/2) = 5/4 × 2 = 10/4 = 2.5।"
    }
